= Strength of Stone =
'''Sphere:''' Special  
'''Level:''' 1  
'''Range:''' 30 yds  
'''Components:''' V, S, M (cross or holy water)  
'''Duration:''' 1 turn  
'''Casting Time:''' 1 turn  
'''Area of Effect:''' 1 creature  
'''Saving Throw:''' None  

== Description ==
Temporarily enhances the recipient’s strength to bend iron or break objects. Grants +1d4 to Strength for 1 turn.

== Special Notes ==
* Treated as a [[Prayer]] in this campaign.
* All casting times and durations are increased by an order of magnitude (round → turn, turn → hour, etc).
* Requires cross and/or holy water.
